name: Yellow dog print
description:
This print is taken from an oil pastel drawing.

It is printed on Hahnemühle paper which I feel is the finest quality acid free archival paper on the market.

The prints are a4 size which is 8.3 x 11.7 inches or 21 x 29.7 centimeters. The actual picture is smaller because I have left a white border for framing.

Each print is signed and shipped in a protective archival acid and lignin free sleeve in a bend-proof mailer.

The last photo shows some original work and some prints in frames.

All of my images are copyright.

Thanks for looking
Vanessa
